        "timestamp": "2020-10-16 12:43:32.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n> \n> Great. Looks better.\n> 2 questions: \n> why SDNR and ORAN are not under CCSDK table ?\nThe same with CDS:\nI wanted to have them a bit more presented as a component under a sepaarate chapter, otherwise you need to know, that they are belonging to CCSDK\n> Why Integration and Modeling are not listed in alphabetical order ?\nI wanted also to destinguish between modules/components (as shown in the architecture picture) and projects/functions. Therefor I separated them and put to the top of the page.\n\nBut I am open for any other suggestions.\nThis will be anyway only a draft version, as not all component content is clarified, so we can discuss this also later (after my next week's vacation)",
